[2025-09-02T07:59:49.344Z] [INFO] Parsed hook input: {
  "session_id": "a3b0aaf9-92df-4ddb-ae70-bb5ddea9c85f",
  "transcript_path": "/Users/jeremyparker/.claude/projects/-Users-jeremyparker-Desktop-Claude-Coding-Projects-sim/a3b0aaf9-92df-4ddb-ae70-bb5ddea9c85f.jsonl",
