    "old_string": "---\ntitle: TypeScript/JavaScript SDK\ndescription: The official TypeScript/JavaScript SDK for Sim\n---",
    "new_string": "---\ntitle: TypeScript SDK\ndescription: Official TypeScript SDK for the Sim API with advanced type safety, generics, and comprehensive workflow management\n---\n\nimport { Tabs, Tab } from 'fumadocs-ui/components/tabs'\nimport { Callout } from 'fumadocs-ui/components/callout'\n\n# TypeScript SDK\n\nThe official Sim TypeScript SDK provides the most comprehensive, type-safe interface to the Sim API. Built specifically for TypeScript projects with advanced generics, strict type checking, and enhanced developer experience.\n\n## Installation\n\n<Tabs items={['npm', 'yarn', 'pnpm', 'bun']}>\n<Tab value=\"npm\">\n```bash\nnpm install @sim/typescript-sdk\n```\n</Tab>\n<Tab value=\"yarn\">\n```bash\nyarn add @sim/typescript-sdk\n```\n</Tab>\n<Tab value=\"pnpm\">\n```bash\npnpm add @sim/typescript-sdk\n```\n</Tab>\n<Tab value=\"bun\">\n```bash\nbun add @sim/typescript-sdk\n```\n</Tab>\n</Tabs>\n\n## Quick Start\n\n### Initialize the Client\n\n```typescript\nimport { SimClient } from '@sim/typescript-sdk';\nimport type { ClientConfig, Workflow } from '@sim/typescript-sdk/types';\n\n// Initialize with full type safety\nconst config: ClientConfig = {\n  apiKey: 'your-api-key',\n  baseUrl: 'https://api.sim.dev',\n  timeout: 30000,\n  retries: 3\n};\n\nconst sim = new SimClient(config);\n\n// Or with environment variable\nconst sim = new SimClient(); // Uses SIM_API_KEY env var\n```\n\n### Basic Operations with Type Safety\n\n```typescript\nimport type { \n  CreateWorkflowRequest, \n  UpdateWorkflowRequest,\n  WorkflowListResponse,\n  WorkflowBlock\n} from '@sim/typescript-sdk/types';\n\n// Create workflow with full type checking\nconst createRequest: CreateWorkflowRequest = {\n  name: 'Data Processing Pipeline',\n  description: 'Processes incoming data',\n  workspaceId: 'ws_abc123',\n  tags: ['data', 'processing'],\n  blocks: [\n    {\n      id: 'api_fetch',\n      type: 'api_call',\n      name: 'Fetch Data',\n      config: {\n        url: 'https://api.example.com/data',\n        method: 'GET'\n      },\n      position: { x: 100, y: 100 }\n    }\n  ]\n};\n\nconst workflow: Workflow = await sim.workflows.create(createRequest);\n\n// Type-safe workflow retrieval\nconst retrieved: Workflow = await sim.workflows.get(workflow.id);\n\n// Type-safe listing with filters\nconst response: WorkflowListResponse = await sim.workflows.list({\n  workspaceId: 'ws_abc123',\n  status: 'active', // TypeScript ensures this is a valid status\n  limit: 20\n});\n```\n\n## Next Steps\n\n- [JavaScript SDK](/docs/sdks/javascript) - Official JavaScript client library\n- [Python SDK](/docs/sdks/python) - Official Python client library  \n- [API Reference](/docs/api/overview) - Complete API documentation\n- [Type Definitions](https://github.com/sim-dev/typescript-sdk/blob/main/src/types.ts) - Complete type definitions"
